h3. Summary

When selecting a specific quick filter on the *Active Sprints* view of a Scrum board or a *Kanban board*, the filter selection is unchecked after navigating away from the board. The same *does not* occur when looking at the *Backlog* view of a Scrum board.
h3. Expected Behavior

Preserve selection of a quick filter in any view of Agile boards.
h3. Actual Behavior

Selection of quick filter is lost when navigating away from the board while on certain views - *Active Sprints* for Scrum boards and *Kanban board*.
h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Navigate to any Agile board;
# If on a Scrum board, go to the *Active Sprints* view;
# Enable one or more Quick Filter/s;
# Click the same board on the *Boards* menu;

h3. Workaround
Other than re-enabling the desired filter/s, there's no known workaround to this problem.

h3. Additional Notes
* Even though {{useStoredSettings=true}} is present in the URL when accessing the board, the Quick Filter preference is not remembered;
* In JIRA Server 7.0.x and earlier releases, this worked fine;

